      <scopecontent id="aspace_9ba795e52a9cd36caa98d3345640dfb0">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Exhibitions and Publications department records consist of general administrative records, correspondence within the Center and with other institutions, publication proofs and records, and documentation of exhibitions held both at the Center and at other institutions to which the Center contributed objects.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <bioghist id="aspace_2e941332d46449a11b4f99ad7078e3f5">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Exhibitions and Publications department directs projects that reach across all curatorial departments. The department manages the Center's exhibitions as well as a publication program, which produces exhibition catalogues and publications on the history of British art.</p>  
      </bioghist>
